tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE telemedicine_billing (
	patient_id INT,
	doctor_id INT,
	appointment_date DATE,
	service_provided TEXT,
	billing_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
	insurance_claim BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE BillingReports (
  report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  provider_id INT,
  patient_id INT,
  service_date DATE,
  total_amount DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE InsuranceClaims (
  claim_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  provider_id INT,
  patient_id INT,
  claim_date DATE,
  diagnosis_code VARCHAR(10),
  claim_amount DECIMAL,
  status VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE TelemedicineServices (
  service_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  provider_id INT,
  patient_id INT,
  service_date DATE,
  service_type VARCHAR(50),
  consultation_fee DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE ComplianceRegulations (
  regulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  regulation_type VARCHAR(50),
  description TEXT,
  compliance_status VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE billing_reports (
    report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id UUID,
    service_provider_id UUID,
    service_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE insurance_claims (
    claim_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id UUID,
    service_provider_id UUID,
    diagnosis_code VARCHAR,
    billed_amount DECIMAL,
    approved_amount DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE telemedicine_services (
    service_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    service_name VARCHAR,
    service_description TEXT,
    service_type VARCHAR,
    service_fee DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR,
    patient_age INTEGER,
    patient_gender VARCHAR,
    insurance_provider VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE service_providers (
    provider_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_name VARCHAR,
    provider_type VARCHAR,
    provider_location VARCHAR,
    provider_contact VARCHAR
);
